b'Research Interests'
b' Electromagnetics as applied to various physical and engineering problems'
b' Miniaturized printed-circuit antennas using 3D metallization for wireless communications'
b' Antenna and circuit applications of advanced artificial materials (metamaterials and EBG materials)'
b' On-chip RF passive designs including inductors, transformers, baluns, and filters for RFIC, and RF interferences with electronics devices.'
